  "description": "Echo resonance pushed to 0.95 — the echolocation filter bank becomes a pitch resonator. At high formant shift the click-train from the hunt macro folds into harmonic partials, and the echo tail blooms into a resonant cloud. The source note is unrecognizable. Only the geometry of the hunt pattern remains: rhythm without time.",
